headline: US oil futures unchanged after API shows big build in U.S. crude inventories
summary: Investing.com -- U.S. crude oil futures were unchanged on from post-settlement levels Tuesday after the American Petroleum Institute reported a much larger build in U.S. weekly crude supplies.
